\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Are you married or are you a widower?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I'm a widower.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And when were you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I was married in - July 1932.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And when were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 19th May 1900.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 South Shields.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember how many years you lived in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Probably six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Can you tell me where you moved to from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Still in South Shields, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you know the street where the first house was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Well the first house was Marshal Wallace Road. Two roomed flat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And the second?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 The second house was in Birchington Avenue.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How long did you live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 About twenty-five years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Until about 1931?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you know why your family made this first move from Marshal War Road?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Requiring - a larger premises for one thing, and a better type, number two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 One sister - oh well, originally two sisters and four brothers. (Including self)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Can you tell me their names and how old they were so as I can get them into or
der? How old was your father when you were born? Or how old was your father when he died and when did he die?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 He was lost at sea in 1918.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you know how old he was then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I rather think he was fifty-eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 So he would be about forty years old when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 That's about it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 The Shetland Islands.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did he come straight from there to South Shields?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Straight to South Shields, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What was his occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 In the Shetland Islands he was a crofter and a fisherman. Here he was the mate of a ship.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What kind of ship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 General cargo.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 A big vessel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 About how many crew, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Probably - oh no, probably be twenty-five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did he have any other jobs apart from those?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did he do any casual work or have any part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you ever remember him being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Only due - during a coal strikes and that sort of thing which temporarily laid off shipping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did this happen very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Two or three times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Any idea how long these periods }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 were}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I - I can remember one strike which was a fairly long duration.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 A few months do you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you know how old your mother was when you were born? Or how old she was when she died and the year when she died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Thirty-eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you know where she came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Wick, in the North of Scotland. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did she have any jobs before she was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did she work after she was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did she have any part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How many rooms were there in the house in Birchington Avenue?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Three rooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 A sitting room, kitchen and a bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did anyone else ever live besides yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your mother pay anybody to help her in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 When you were about six years old you moved to Birchington Avenue?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How long did you stay there until you moved to another one in the same avenue?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Maybe ten years I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 When you were about fifteen or sixteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was the washing done at home or sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 At home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your mother or your father mend or make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Mother would mend clothes. And father was capable of repairing shoes. Beyond that no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember if the clothes that you had were always new or were they sometimes second hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Handed down perhaps, but not actually secondhand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Any idea where your clothes were bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 The place where I worked for fifty years. Yes. William Wood and Son, Commercial Road. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And even before you worked there you used to buy things there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What kind of place is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 A tailors and outfitters. Manufacturing and retail. A fairly big business, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was there any special time when you were a child that you were bought clothes or did you just have them bought when they were needed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I would say when they were needed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What about shoes, were they always bought new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Sometimes handed down but - only within the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Where did you buy your shoes, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 My maternal grandfather - had a footwear shop and we got them there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was there any special time of the year when everybody bought new shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I always got a new pair on the day of my birth. Yes. As a birthday gift. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house like cleaning and cooking and washing up and making fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Oh yes, he was a very capable man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 All those things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was he able to do things like decorating and repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No, he was away too much for that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 So when he was home he did the small jobs round the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 When you were quite small do you remember him ever bathing you or helping you get dressed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did he read to you? Or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember him taking you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Where did you go, what kind of places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I can remember one occasion quite clearly when he took us to see and hear Harry Lauder. Yes. A very favourite comedian of his, naturally.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did he ever look after you at home when your mother was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I can't say that that lot ever fell to him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you have any little jobs in the house that you always had to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Oh yes, several little jobs. Cleaning cutlery, getting the coal in. Sweeping up generally, that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember how long you carried on doing these jobs, after you left school or until you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Until I left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Then you didn't do them anymore?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What about your brothers and sisters, did they have similar jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We took it in turn - with these jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did they stop doing them when they started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 They would cease doing it then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember the older children helping the younger ones with things that they found difficult, like ge
tting dressed and cutting up touch meat and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Oh yes. Yes, it was a very united family in that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you notice the younger ones helping the older ones with things ever?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I suppose that we did - as far as we were able.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Apart from getting dressed and eating can you think of any other ways in which the children helped each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I - I think principally - when you had to go out it was a case of looking after each other, older ones looking after younger ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We did retire reasonably early.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you know what time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I would say half past nine to ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 When you were about what age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Oh about the age of ten onward.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 When you were about five or six when you first started school, did your mother still put you to bed then do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No, I think we were capable of looking after ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember how old you were when you first went to bed on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I don't remember clearly, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you share the bedroom or share your bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We had to, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Can you tell me what the sleeping arrangements were, was it two boys in a bed or three of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Two - sometimes three. According to the premises which we lived in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 But in the first house in Birchington Avenue, you shared the bedroom with your three brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And your sister would be in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 In the room with mother.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What about having a bath, did you have any room for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 
We had an improvised bath, a zinc affair. And that was filled by hand and emptied by hand. But it was used regularly. At least once a week anyhow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Where did you put it when you were using it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 It was in the back kitchen. Well I think there was a - a sort of a cooking stove in there which kept the place reasonable warm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you have a particular day when you all put clean clothes on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did we? Oh yes. Oh yes. I would think that we changed approximately once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Where did the family eat their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were there any occasions when they ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 In the back kitchen, or the scullery, whichever you like to call it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What did she cook on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 A gas cooker. Yes. Yes, yes. Prior to that of course it was a fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 But in 1906 she had a gas cooker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Well probably later - for the gas cooker. I'm not quite sure if gas cookers were in then. No. No, I think in the first house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What time of the day did you used to have breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 About eight to half past.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Who used to be present for that meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Mother and the rest of the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Not usually father?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What was the commonest food and drink at breakfast time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Porridge. Tea. Bread and butter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were there any days when you different breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Fairly similar each day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What about midday meals, where did you eat the midday meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 All the family together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Until we started work. We were all - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What were some of the commoner things you had at lunchtime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Scotch broth with dumplings. Sheep}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715  head broth. Yes. Generally thought the - the type of family meal that was inexpensive and would share out fairly well. And followed by some form of sweet. A rice pudding or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was there any day when you had anything different for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Perhaps on a Sunday when it would go to a roast and a Yorkshire pudding - and be perhaps a little more extensive than during the week.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 The traditional sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What time would you have the evening meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 The evening meal would be, I think about eight o'clock, and would be just a light meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Cup of cocoa. Bread and butter }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 or}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715  a scone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you have anything between the lunch and evening meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 There was always the afternoon tea when you came in from school.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What did you get for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Bread and butter, scone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 So very similar meals at half past four and at eight o'clock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 The evening meal on Saturdays or Sundays, were they any different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No different. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What did you have to drink with your meals, with lunch or tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Lunch no, unless water. The evening meal might be a cup of cocoa.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your mother or father bake their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Always. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Your mother would?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your father ever bake?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No, no. Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did she make jam or bottle fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Made jam but not bottle fruit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did she make pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Wine, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did she ever make medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Wine - bee wine. Yes. You've never hear of it? It's a sort of a - 
a vegetable thing that - used to ferment and it would ascend and sink in this big earthenware jam. It was called bee wine. I don't know that it was intoxicating, it was made with a lot of sugar and yeast. But quite harmless. Bee wine.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did she make any medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Nothing apart from the home aperient. Such as the senna tea. Epsom salts with cream of tartar and lemon. But nothing apart from that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did she ever brew any beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did they grow vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. We had no garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did they buy fresh vegetables and fruit or did they buy tinned or dried ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Fresh vegetables. And fruit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 You wouldn't have any livestock because you had no garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No livestock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember how many times a week you ate meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Almost every day. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was it fresh meat or was it sometimes tinned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Fresh meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you ever get any extra meat from activities such as poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I never remember getting any. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember seeing your mother having less food so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 
Yes. During strike periods - when - money was not available to - to buy - as much food as we needed. And - then - mother would - deprive herself so that we should be well fed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your father have more food than the rest of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. Only in keeping with his stature I would think, but not otherwise.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were you allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what there was or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Largely we had what was given. Very rarely we complained - we - we weren't expected to complain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What was your }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 parent\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715  attitude if you left some food uneaten on the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 plate}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 A little concerned perhaps, in case we were unwell. But otherwise I think they understood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 They weren't annoyed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 If there was something on the table you wanted like the salt could you ask someone to pass it or did you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 wait}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715  until it was passed or did you reach over and get it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We would ask for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Could you ask for second helpings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We were expected to hold them in a fairly civilised way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes, oh yes, sit up to the table. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Could you bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Reasonably when you were finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 You didn't have to wait until everyone else was finished?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you have to repeat a magic formula?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No, we didn't have anything of that. You slid off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did all the family sit at the table for the meal and did you always have the same places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I think practically the same, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Who used to serve the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What order were you served in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I think - I think just clockwise.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Just clockwise?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 She didn't start with anyone in particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Where did the younger brothers and sisters sit before they could feed themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I think a baby's chair, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And who fed them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Mother. Or - my sister as she - as she grew.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember how old the younger children were when they were able to join in the family meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Well I think we would join in the family when we're about five years of age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Very easy indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was she an affectionate person?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Very.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 If you had any worries could you share them with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How about your father, was he an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 
Quite easy to talk to. And mixed well with us, but of course, being so often away - we enjoyed a greater freedom with mother. That was obvious.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 But would you describe your father as affectionate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And you could take your worries to him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Quite easily, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I think they expected - politeness - or never to be rude and to treat them with something of the affection they shared with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did they bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 They did, they brought us up in a very happy family way and we - very rarely indeed, if ever, had rows. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did they say that you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I don't think we - we were counseled as such but I'm quite certain that we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you know what kind of people you think your parents hoped you would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 
I think they hoped - that we would be reasonably educated. I think that they would certainly wish that we had some form of religious background. And that - in the main like we should be ordinarily decent people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were there certain things that they thought were very important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I - I don't think anything essentially important other than essential kindness.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What did they think about swearing?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 It was something that was never used in our home. Parents nev
er used it and - therefore I don't think there was ever any opinion expressed about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Not usually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 If you did something that your parented didn't like, what happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Sometimes - physical punishment, but nothing very severe. And then only - administered by mother, never by father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How did she administer it, what form did it take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Oh the back of the hairbrush on your bottom. But it didn't do us any harm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How often was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Can you remember any particular occasion when you got the back of the hairbrush?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. I don't think I can.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Would you say that you received the ideas about how to behave from both your parents or did one play a more important part than the other?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I think mother played the more important part, probably because - she was more nearly with us with father being seafaring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 When you had a birthday was it different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Oh yes. Birthday - a birthday cake would be made and we would be }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 counseled}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715  to visit our relatives, particularly those who were sufficiently affluent - tell them that it was the birthday and - we would get some gift. It might only be small but we always got a gift. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 And as I say, from my maternal grandparent I - I would always get a pair of shoes and I must admit also that - I wore some of the quaintest styles in my - in my early days. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 On the principle that you can't look a gift horse in the mouth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you ever have guests to tea on your birthday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. Cousins and - nearby friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Can you remember anything that you did with your father or mother together on Christmas Day?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Not particularly together because father didn't have many Christmases with us. But a
lways - particularly in the early days - the opening - of your stocking, your Christmas stocking, and taking out the various little gifts. Fruit, nuts, chocolate, so forth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 That was always together with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 In later years we had a - an American organ and then after that a piano.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Who used to play them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I used to play and my sister used to play. I believe I got the organ for my - twenty-first birthday. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was there anyone in the family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I belonged the choir. My sister belonged the choir. My father had quite a nice voice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We did. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Not unless it was a game of cards, such as whist. Or - where there'd be a number of people sharing the game.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. Juvenile books. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 Those paper backed ones like the Magnet and the Gem. }
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 You won't remember them. Yes. Books like that. And then later on, school boy books. Prizes that we would get at Sunday school and in day school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Just perhaps the evening - local paper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 You didn't have a daily one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Sunday papers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Any magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember your mother or father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Not a great deal I wouldn't think, their life was very busy without that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your mother ever read to you? Or did your mother read to your father or the other way round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Can you remember a funeral in the family when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I can remember my - maternal grandparent when I was fairly young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Can you tell me who attended the funeral and the kind of clothes they wore?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 In t
hose days - well, all of the relatives attended. A few of the neighbours. And in those days - it was a heavy type of mourning consisting principally of black. Even children - were dressed in black.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were you taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relations ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Neighbours occasionally. Relatives, fairly frequently.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Who took you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did she ever take you shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Your father didn't take you shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 You went with your father to the theatre, can you think of any other places you went with your father, just with your father alone?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 When he was home, regularly - to morning church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Any other outings with your parents, for example, Bank Holiday time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Principally go the beach - where we had picnic food and spend the whole of the day. Sometimes with father also.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Which beach did you go to, near here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Our local beach.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What's that called?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 The Trollocks. No, you don't know. And - then - at the other end where th
e pier is. And the beach - and the total - the length of the beach was about a mile. It's still a good beach, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you ever go away for a holiday when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I think the first holiday that I really had would be when I go with the boys Brigade to camp.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How old were you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Twelve - thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 For how long did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 One week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you go regularly then from twelve upwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. Oh yes. Year by year to a place called Stocksfield. Yes. Not very far from Tyne. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Any other holidays, perhaps with your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Later on - we would hire a cottage near to Branton and then - the members of the family that were available would go into this cottage.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 This is when you were how old?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Seventeen - eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Just towards the end of the war?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What kind of things did you do at Brampton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We played tennis, we went rambling, we did a bit of fishing, bit of rowing. Token Todd. Quite a big sort of lake. Well we did rowing and
 fishing there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How did you spend Saturdays when you were a boy at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 
Saturdays principally playing football. Sundays essentially a church day. The whole day. Bible class in the morning, morning church, afternoon Sunday school and evening church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you wear special clothes on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We always had a Sunday suit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And you kept it on all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes, until you come home. Then change.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you ever play any games on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your parents think it was wrong to play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 The general opinion was that it was wrong to play games.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What about working on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 We never worked on Sundays either.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your parents go to church with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What denomination did you attend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Baptist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 You went every week and three times each Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And your father always went when he was home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And everyone in the family went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Everybody attended the church, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were there any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. Day trips - to a nearby country spot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 How often were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Once a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Any other social activities organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Whist drives and social evenings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Would you take part in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes. With a little bit of dancing thrown in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you say you belonged to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I did. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Apart from }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 singing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715  on Sundays did the choir do anything else? You had practices?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Oh yes, once a week. And the choir used to run a yearly dance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Any other clubs organised by the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Boys Brigade. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3501630\charrsid2905715 Junior}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715  Guild, Senior Guild.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Which of these did you belong to, the Boys Brigade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Boys Brigade and the Senior Guild. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 And the Junior Guild before that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Junior Guild before that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What were these Guilds?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 
Well - just a - a meeting for - for the young people where they would play games perhaps and finish up with - some little religious service. And - and probably have a - a light meal - light refreshments.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 By whom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 It was shared.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 In turn or all together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Different turns. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 No. Apart from privately. Yes, but it wasn't a communal affair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did you ever have any communal prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Not - not in that sense - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 But you were taught to say prayers on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Did your father have any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Have you any idea what his views were at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I would think that he would be Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Could you suggest why he might be a Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 I think - perhaps that it was then a Liberal borough. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 What about your mother, do you know anything about her political views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11864399 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 She wouldn't have any decided - politic - policy in that direction but - I should think that she would vote Liberal too.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 Do you remember either them voting in a general election before 19-9?
