ffair because my mother had died some six months previously. But - very happy event and - we were married by the minister of our church who was very dear friend of mine. I shall never forget him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4725300 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6046477\charrsid2905715 You were married at your church?
